{
  "texts": [
    "However, I have made changes to the exercise to reduce the probability of ChatGPT discovering it on the internet.Write a python code to find the answer to the following programming exercise.We have a number of baskets.",
    "Each basket has two compartments.",
    "We have made a list of all of the items currently in each basket (your puzzle input), but we need help finding the errors.",
    "Every item type is identified by a single lowercase or uppercase letter (that is, a and A refer to different types of items).Every item type can be converted to a priority.",
    "Lowercase item types a through z have priorities 1 through 26."
  ]
}